EVENTMORALACT

NAME
        eventMoralAct()

SYNOPSIS
        int eventMoralAct(int degree)

DESCRIPTION
        Adds the integer "degree" to the creature's morality.

EXAMPLES
        Killing a smurf might do this: gargamel->eventMoralAct(-50)

LOCATION
        /lib/classes


SEE ALSO
        SetMorality, GetMorality, GetMoralityDescription

Author
        Cratylus

